            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>[This is the t]ombstone of ..., son of Yehudah,<lb/>[who died] on the fourth day
                    (Wednesday)<lb/>...................in the month Elul<lb/>..................the
                    year<lb/>...................[and ei]ght years<lb/>[of the destruction] of the
                    Sanctuary. May it be rebuilt<lb/>[.....may it be awakened] to the voice
                    of<lb/>[the announcer of peace]. Peace.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p> Lines 6-8 are in Hebrew. Dated to ? Elul, [..]8 E.D.S, Wednesday</p>
            </div>
